    "body": "Workaround: plot the shared axis' data to the new axis, clear the new axis, then plot the new data to the new axis\n\n```\nimport pylab\nimport pandas as pd\npylab.ion(); pylab.show()\nidx1 = pd.date_range('2015-01-01', periods=3, freq='1M')\nidx2 = idx1[:1] + idx1[2:]\nseries1 = pd.Series(range(len(idx1)), idx1)\nseries2 = pd.Series(range(len(idx2)), idx2)\n\npylab.figure()\nax1 = pylab.subplot(211)\nseries1.plot(ax=ax1)\nax2 = pylab.subplot(212, sharex=ax1)\nseries1.plot(ax=ax2)\nax2.clear()\nseries2.plot(ax=ax2)\n```\n"
